Package: ORFquant
Title: Splice-aware Quantification of ORF translation
Author: Lorenzo Calviello [aut,cre], Uwe Ohler [rev,fnd]
Maintainer: Lorenzo Calviello <calviello.l.bio@gmail.com>
Description: ORFquant is a method that annotates and quantifies translation at the single ORF level using Ribo-seq data.
Depends: R (>= 3.6.0), rtracklayer, BSgenome, Biostrings, GenomicFeatures, multitaper, GenomicAlignments, GenomicFiles, ggplot2, cowplot, grid, BiocGenerics, knitr, gridExtra, rmarkdown
Imports: BiocParallel, GenomicRanges, Rsamtools, magrittr, tidyr, methods
Suggests: devtools, testthat, Gviz
License: GPL-3 or above
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: FALSE
biocViews: RiboSeq, GenomeAnnotation, Transcriptomics, Software
Name: ORFquant
Version: 1.2.0
RoxygenNote: 7.3.0
